{"blogid": "125697834", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "2", "writerCollect": "2", "writerComment": "0", "writerFan": "1", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "22", "writerName": "想摆烂的小陈", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_125697834.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "188246", "writerRankWeekly": "1463658", "writerThumb": "2", "writerVisitNum": "1914", "blog_read_count": "1187", "blog_time": "已于 2022-07-10 00:07:05 修改", "blog_title": "Cmake如何更新版本", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h1><a id=\"Cmake_0\"></a><strong>Cmake如何更新版本</strong></h1>\n<p>​ <strong>去官网下载已经编译好的包</strong></p>\n<p>​ <a href=\"https://cmake.org/download/\">Cmake官网链接</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\acfbb094f4c449d49273871f24f00a7d.jpeg\"/></p>\n<p>​ 选择对应的的系统与架构，比如我如果更新的是NX，那我就选择下载<strong>cmake-3.24.0-rc3-linux-aarch64.tar.gz</strong>这个压缩包，虚拟机则下载<strong>cmake-3.24.0-rc3-linux-x86_64.tar.gz</strong></p>\n<p>​ <strong>将包解压到你想存放解压文件的目录</strong>**</p>\n<p>​ 然后进入到你解压的文件夹下的bin目录下</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-C\">cd /解压的文件夹名/bin/\n</code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>执行以下指令</p>\n<p>./cmake --version</p>\n<p>cmake --version</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\d8bf4befa98c43f4ba13697f2107a6c3.jpeg\"/></p>\n<pre><code>可以看出现在我们cmake版本为3.16.3，而我们需要更新的cmake版本为3.24.0\n</code></pre>\n<p>​ <strong>建立软链接</strong></p>\n<p>​ 先将我们久版本的cmake进行删除</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-C\">sudo apt-get autoremove cmake\n</code></pre>\n<p>​ 接下来将我们新版本的cmake链接上去</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-C\">sudo ln -sf /cmake解压文件夹名/bin/* /usr/bin/\n即你的包的绝对路径\n</code></pre>\n<p>​<br/> 至此你的cmake版本就已经更新完成了，为了验证我们输入以下指令</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-C\">cmake --version\n</code></pre>\n<p>​ <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\3574959a100145728768ac941f7e4c0e.jpeg\"/></p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Others", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-07-10 00:07:05", "summary": "如何更新版本去官网下载已经编译好的包官网链接在这里插入图片描述选择对应的的系统与架构，比如我如果更新的是，那我就选择下载这个压缩包，虚拟机则下载将包解压到你想存放解压文件的目录然后进入到你解压的文件夹"}